{"tid":234463,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"唔為HA發聲冇資格係香港夾band","createTime":"2017-05-08T10:17:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-10T23:25:03.000Z","uid":35136,"like":52,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b5ee31cca7be58402a061746c52c936e560af445","tid":234463,"uid":35136,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T10:17:36.000Z","msg":"Hidden Agenda 咁樣被人踩上門拉人封舖真係好撚嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nHidden Agenda一直都係獨立樂隊嘅聖地 啲大band唔多唔少都有去過玩或者去過聽live 好多大band由獨立樂隊出身 都不時支持本土獨立樂隊 咁今次HA被人踩到上面係咪更加應該出聲 運用佢哋嘅影響力等公眾關注香港獨立樂隊嘅問題呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nHA冇錯係一直游走法律邊緣 你可能對於上咗岸嘅樂隊可能身份問題要獨善其身 但HA犯嘅係一條跟唔上時代嘅戇鳩法例 如果冇呢種反建制嘅勇氣就根本冇咗搖滾嘅靈魂 做Dear Jane唔講政治玩情歌算啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港咁多隊band搞關注組又好 作隻歌又好 舊曲改詞又好 fb出post都好 唔為HA表態發聲冇資格係香港夾band<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2601e456eeb5b6afca0796724136b64fb4ff092b","tid":234463,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T10:35:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c9b545e8a9095688a2d2781c1a5e7ef27395ca","tid":234463,"uid":27963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T10:45:49.000Z","msg":"唉..."},{"pid":"3558ad381d25e1d69654488f47020c79cce7785e","tid":234463,"uid":96117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T10:56:03.000Z","msg":"無架啦<br />\n成班港豬聽kpop之嘛<br />\n出面發生緊咩事都唔知啦"},{"pid":"2cccbde85943f5876ed7c171fc409b384614d788","tid":234463,"uid":49144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T11:02:20.000Z","msg":"dear jane<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"147c9febe26fff50697a877753649ba609e8adf3","tid":234463,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T11:05:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無架啦<br />\n成班港豬聽kpop之